videos.description: Villanova guard Phil Booth picks off the pass and finishes the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Booth gets the steal and finishes through the contact

videos.description: Georgetown's James Akinjo gives the Hoyas a one-point halftime lead with a 3-pointer right at the buzzer.
videos.headline: Akinjo drains 3 at the end of the half

videos.description: With the ball loose and players all over the court, Phil Booth is able to get the pass and knock down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Broken play leads to a Phil Booth 3-pointer
